(299, 1, '2025-01-10 15:13:58', '2025-01-10 15:13:58', '<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[ux_gallery ids=\"289,290,298,292,291,286,287,284,285,297,276,273,294,293,295,296,274,279,278,277,282,283,281,280,272,288,275\" lightbox_image_size=\"original\" type=\"masonry\" width=\"full-width\" col_spacing=\"xsmall\" animate=\"fadeInRight\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'GALLERY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-01-10 15:13:58', '2025-01-10 15:13:58', '', 70, 'http://atpcgi.com/?p=299', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(267, 1, '2025-01-10 13:53:52', '2025-01-10 13:53:52', '<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[ux_gallery ids=\"48,27,47,45,44,245,246,32,36,28,29,30,31,14,15,49,266,247,260,255,262,263,34,35\" lightbox_image_size=\"original\" type=\"masonry\" width=\"full-width\" col_spacing=\"xsmall\" animate=\"fadeInRight\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'GALLERY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-01-10 13:53:52', '2025-01-10 13:53:52', '', 70, 'http://atpcgi.com/?p=267', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(268, 1, '2025-01-10 14:19:47', '2025-01-10 14:19:47', '<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"47\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>EXTERIOR</p>\n<p>We primarily produce exterior renders for developers and architects, in order to give them a better idea of how the buildings are going to look in various environments. A lot of attention is dedicated to the artistic and compositional aspects of the images, in order for the visualization to be not only technically accurate but also visually attractive</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>INTERIOR</p>\n<p>We strive to devote individual attention to each and every image and treat every project with as much care as possible in order to deliver the best results. Most requests for our interior renders come from interior designers, marketing, and real estate agencies.</p>\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[row_inner]\n\n[col_inner span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"15\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>VR</p>\n<p>Thanks to their unique and broad perspective, our 360° VR tours provide a detailed and in-depth overview of exterior and interior areas of our projects. Our VR tours are great for marketing and presentations and are often requested by real-estate and advertisement agencies.</p>\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"260\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"32\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>ANIMATION</p>\n<p>Animation - is the best way to bring a project to life and show its best features in an artistic and informative way. Only a team of great artists and technical specialists can handle such a complex task and we are prepared to tackle even the most ambitious projects.</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '193-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-01-10 14:19:47', '2025-01-10 14:19:47', '', 193, 'http://atpcgi.com/?p=268', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(269, 1, '2025-01-10 14:27:32', '2025-01-10 14:27:32', '<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[ux_slider timer=\"3000\"]\n\n[ux_banner height=\"100%\" height__sm=\"56.25%\" video_mp4=\"http://atpcgi.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ex20001_2.mp4\" video_visibility=\"visible\"]\n\n[text_box width__sm=\"60\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\"]\n\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n[ux_image id=\"32\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"36\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n\n[/ux_slider]\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'HOME', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-01-10 14:27:32', '2025-01-10 14:27:32', '', 127, 'http://atpcgi.com/?p=269', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(271, 1, '2025-01-10 14:42:36', '2025-01-10 14:42:36', '<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[ux_gallery ids=\"270,27,47,45,44,245,246,32,36,28,29,30,31,14,15,49,266,247,260,255,262,263,34,35\" lightbox_image_size=\"original\" type=\"masonry\" width=\"full-width\" col_spacing=\"xsmall\" animate=\"fadeInRight\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'GALLERY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-01-10 14:42:36', '2025-01-10 14:42:36', '', 70, 'http://atpcgi.com/?p=271', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(302, 1, '2025-01-10 15:16:31', '2025-01-10 15:16:31', '<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[ux_slider timer=\"3000\"]\n\n[ux_banner height=\"100%\" height__sm=\"56.25%\" video_mp4=\"http://atpcgi.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ex20001_2.mp4\" video_visibility=\"visible\"]\n\n[text_box width__sm=\"60\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\"]\n\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n[ux_image id=\"300\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"291\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"297\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n\n[/ux_slider]\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'HOME', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-01-10 15:16:31', '2025-01-10 15:16:31', '', 127, 'http://atpcgi.com/?p=302', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(303, 1, '2025-01-10 15:18:38', '2025-01-10 15:18:38', '<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"298\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>EXTERIOR</p>\n<p>We primarily produce exterior renders for developers and architects, in order to give them a better idea of how the buildings are going to look in various environments. A lot of attention is dedicated to the artistic and compositional aspects of the images, in order for the visualization to be not only technically accurate but also visually attractive</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>INTERIOR</p>\n<p>We strive to devote individual attention to each and every image and treat every project with as much care as possible in order to deliver the best results. Most requests for our interior renders come from interior designers, marketing, and real estate agencies.</p>\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[row_inner]\n\n[col_inner span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"276\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>VR</p>\n<p>Thanks to their unique and broad perspective, our 360° VR tours provide a detailed and in-depth overview of exterior and interior areas of our projects. Our VR tours are great for marketing and presentations and are often requested by real-estate and advertisement agencies.</p>\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"273\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"289\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>ANIMATION</p>\n<p>Animation - is the best way to bring a project to life and show its best features in an artistic and informative way. Only a team of great artists and technical specialists can handle such a complex task and we are prepared to tackle even the most ambitious projects.</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '193-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-01-10 15:18:38', '2025-01-10 15:18:38', '', 193, 'http://atpcgi.com/?p=303', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
